headline: Is U.S. Bancorp's (USB) Digital Asset Custody Push Shaping Its Role in Financial Innovation?
summary: U.S. Bancorp recently announced the redemption of all outstanding 5.727% Fixed-to-Floating Rate Senior Notes due October 2026, with payment to be made through The Depository Trust Company; in addition, the company has been selected as custodian for Anchorage Digital Bank's stablecoin reserve funds, reflecting new opportunities in digital asset services. This move into digital asset custody underscores U.S. Bancorp's increasing involvement in the evolving financial technology landscape,...
